        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3665499870" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14298903106341911200"><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/261240.The_Cask_of_Amontillado' title='The Cask of Amontillado by Edgar Allan Poe' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Cask of Amontillado</a> by <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4624490.Edgar_Allan_Poe' title='Edgar Allan Poe' rel='nofollow noopener'>Edgar Allan Poe</a><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1606477203i/30435446._SX540_.jpg' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/>A short piece of writing and the story was strange. But it possessed some dark, creepy, morbid ideas, which might be distressing for some readers. Mainly, It&apos;s a short tale about hatred. And that story showed the darkest side of humankind. However, I had to read the story several times for better understanding.<br/><blockquote>
  <i>A million candles have burned themselves out. Still I read on. </i>
</blockquote><br/><i>A bit complicated.</i></span>
  <span id="freeText14298903106341911200" style="display:none"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/261240.The_Cask_of_Amontillado" title="The Cask of Amontillado by Edgar Allan Poe" rel="nofollow noopener">The Cask of Amontillado</a> by <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4624490.Edgar_Allan_Poe" title="Edgar Allan Poe" rel="nofollow noopener">Edgar Allan Poe</a><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1606477203i/30435446._SX540_.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br>A short piece of writing and the story was strange. But it possessed some dark, creepy, morbid ideas, which might be distressing for some readers. Mainly, It's a short tale about hatred. And that story showed the darkest side of humankind. However, I had to read the story several times for better understanding.<br><blockquote>
  <i>A million candles have burned themselves out. Still I read on. </i>
</blockquote><br><i>A bit complicated.</i></span>
